 Function:     0, Int 2Fh
 Description:  Verifies that MVSOUND.SYS is loaded.
 Calling:      ax = BC00h
               bx = '??'
               cx = 0
               dx = 0
 Returns:      xor bx, cx
               xor bx, dx
               bx = 'MV' if MVSOUND.SYS is installed

